item.title: An Intro to Workspace ONE Hub Templates
item.author: partheeban.kandasamy@gmail.com
item.description: Hi! I’m Nagul Subramanian working on VMware End User Computing technologies for more than 7 years and have gained a lot of field experience on WS ONE and Mobility. I’ve always had a personal goal to contribute my knowledge back to the community. As I explored ways to do that, I ran into PK and Cloud Tekki. This is my first blog post(hopefully first of many) and would love to hear your feedback!
